name: gamelist_(GET)

Success 200.description: e.g. Group A Match, Semi-Final, etc

title: Login
name: login_(POST)
description: Inform server of facebook id after login on device

Parameter.description: Name of user as displayed on facebook

Success 200.description: Other parameters to be determined at a later time

title: Get Updates
name: getUpdates_(SOCKET)
description: Get all updates after specified time. APP TO GAME SERVER

Parameter.description: Name of method as defined above

DataObject.description: Unix timestamp of the time since last update

Success 200.description: A sequence (or array?) of socket messages for newQuestion, newAnswer and scoreUpdate types

title: New Answer
name: newAnswer_(SOCKET)
description: New answer posted on server. GAME SERVER BROADCAST

Parameter.description: Name of method as defined above

title: New Question
name: newQuestion_(SOCKET)
description: New question posted on server. GAME SERVER BROADCAST

Parameter.description: Name of method as defined above

DataObject.description: Amount of time provided for answering question
Correct answer id if known, 0 otherwise
Unix timestamp of the time at which question was posted
Score at the time of the question

title: User Answer
name: userAnswer_(SOCKET)
description: Submit a user answer to the server. APP TO GAME SERVER

Parameter.description: Name of method as defined above
